{% doc %}
  @prompt
    You are a senior Shopify OS 2.0 theme developer.
    Using the attached reference screenshot, create a custom Shopify section that displays a UGC / community photo gallery exactly like the design shown.
    
    Section Layout:
    
    Centered section heading text at the top:
    
    “Tag us in your posts to get featured here!”
    
    Below the heading, display a grid of square images
    
    Grid layout:
    
    3 columns × 2 rows on desktop (total 6 images visible)
    
    Equal image sizes and spacing
    
    Image Card Design:
    
    Each item contains:
    
    A single image (user-generated content)
    
    Images should:
    
    Be square
    
    Use object-fit: cover
    
    Fill the entire grid cell
    
    Subtle border radius
    
    Clean, edge-to-edge visual layout
    
    Hover & Interaction (Desktop):
    
    On hover:
    
    Slight zoom-in effect on image
    
    Optional dark overlay fade
    
    Cursor should indicate click if image has link
    
    Responsiveness:
    
    Desktop: 3 columns
    
    Tablet: 2 columns
    
    Mobile: 1 column OR 2-column grid (configurable)
    
    Maintain equal aspect ratio across breakpoints
    
    Shopify Section Requirements:
    
    Use Liquid + JSON schema
    
    Use repeatable blocks for images
    
    Each block should allow:
    
    Image picker
    
    Optional link URL (Instagram post or product page)
    
    Section settings should include:
    
    Heading text
    
    Grid gap spacing
    
    Border radius control
    
    Top and bottom padding
    
    Code Output Rules:
    
    Provide complete Shopify section code
    
    Include:
    
    HTML (Liquid)
    
    CSS inside {% style %} tags
    
    JSON schema
    
    Code must be copy-paste ready
    
    Use pure CSS (no JS required)
    
    Follow Shopify OS 2.0 best practices
    
    Match grid spacing, image proportions, and overall layout as closely as possible to the reference screenshot.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-ugc-gallery-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: {{ block.settings.padding_top }}px 0 {{ block.settings.padding_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-ugc-gallery__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
  
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .ai-ugc-gallery__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.heading_spacing }}px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
  }

  .ai-ugc-gallery__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: {{ block.settings.grid_gap }}px;
  }

  .ai-ugc-gallery__item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.border_radius }}px;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
  }

  .ai-ugc-gallery__link-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    position: relative;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .ai-ugc-gallery__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-ugc-gallery__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
  }

  .ai-ugc-gallery__link-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-ugc-gallery__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .ai-ugc-gallery__overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .ai-ugc-gallery__link-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-ugc-gallery__overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .ai-ugc-gallery__placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
  }

  .ai-ugc-gallery__placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 50%;
    height: 50%;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .ai-ugc-gallery__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-ugc-gallery__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.columns_mobile }}, 1fr);
    }

    .ai-ugc-gallery__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.heading_size }}px * 0.75);
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

